 I (ERNEST RUTHERFORD) CAME INTO THE ROOM, WHICH WAS HALF DARK, AND PRESENTLY
 SPOTTED LORD KELVIN IN THE AUDIENCE AND REALIZED I WAS IN TROUBLE AT
